Package: greenR
Title: Green Index Quantification, Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.0.0.9
Authors@R:
    person("Sachit", "Mahajan", , "sachitmahajan90@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9558-8895"))
Description: This package that enables the quantification, analysis, and visualization of urban greenness within city networks. It leverages data from OpenStreetMap (www.openstreetmap.org) and is implemented as both an R package and a Shiny web application for user-friendly interaction.
